Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三界层是炎热的灼热世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.30,0:01:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配著铁板村的玛利亚妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.94,0:01:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把地面的温度上升\N令村民受苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.90,0:01:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为地面是铁板的关系\N真令人受不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里我们得到了\N很重要的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.84,0:01:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灼热地狱之迷便藏在\N极寒之剑和灼热之盾身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也会是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.50,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十三话\N燃烧的斗魂\N九九八十一攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁说可以休息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起,请让我饮水吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.18,0:03:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水?你口渴了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.68,0:03:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.50,0:03:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?那便特别地\N请你喝这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时一支是要100元的\N我真是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在免费给你喝饮\N怎么?很高兴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?这么好喝的东西\N现在可以免费饮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴吧?\N来,喝吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.84,0:03:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚意推推介熔岩饮品,说笑罢\N怎么?精神了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没精神的人\N我随时也会给他喝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了,快去工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.09,0:04:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热…我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底在想什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…给我水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.82,0:04:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔,我肚子饿了\N吃热热的火锅鸟东吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热,走开啊,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃火锅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,古拿玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.94,0:04:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拿玛,你有水吗?\N分点给我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.78,0:04:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.32,0:04:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好,全部喝掉了\N真对不起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.40,0:04:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样吧,我们是同伴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一个人喝,真过份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,这是由我找到的水啊\N这么想要的话自己去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样说话吧\N不是太薄情了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说如果我有困难时\N你们会来救我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.39,0:05:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说我不要这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恢复原来很有型的男子\N你们会帮我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,什么也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有海的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海?在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害,海在燃烧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片火红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.01,0:05:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.63,0:05:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是热岛,因为太过热\N现在好像没人住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.11,0:05:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能极寒之剑和灼热之盾\N会在那个岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.90,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但怎样过去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.96,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许只有你才能渡过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你叫渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!那边有个村\N去看看吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.96,0:06:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我们分头收集情报吧\N顺便找水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.93,0:06:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.32,0:06:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位村民，我今天也带了\N美味的熔岩饮料来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.26,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也好像很想要呢\N好,第一个便是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!你想要多少支?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.68,0:06:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?你想要十支?\N是吗?一支是1000元…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是100元吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.25,0:06:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么十支是一万五千元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我二万元吗?\N好,这里十支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.31,0:07:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…找钱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.69,0:07:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找钱?你说什么?\N老头子,一支一千元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十支当然是二万元了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.42,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!大叔\N你要多少支熔岩饮料?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在卖果汁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你,太太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要!我要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…在下也想要那个饮品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.33,0:07:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?是客人吗?\N好,想要多少支?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一支便够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.50,0:07:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣…好辣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.28,0:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.86,0:08:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟喝那不能喝的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能喝的东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.56,0:08:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫熔岩饮料的是\N辣得不能喝下的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.58,0:08:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第三界层的常识啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有点料子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要多支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前请你先付钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.77,0:08:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?\N大叔你好像在生气呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在生气啊\N我最讨厌没钱的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.40,0:08:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,这大叔不送我果汁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡?你便是叫渡的小鬼吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.10,0:08:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,竟卖这样的东西\N还要收钱,太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?\N这个小鬼不是喝得很高兴吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,很好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.61,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个虽然是\N火美子是特别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村内的人不是很困惑吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.60,0:09:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!我已等你好久了\N为了和你决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已准备了特别的擂台\N在那处决胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.50,0:09:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜…不行呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我接受你挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有骨气的小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你放开火美子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口,想我放了她的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便把她和那大叔喝的\N熔岩饮料钱交出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.21,0:09:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,一支要一千元\N两支便是三千元了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.92,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算错了吧?一支是一千元\N两支便是两千元啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?你说我算错了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这么简单的数\N也算不到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!我从小算数便最差了\N可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我最讨厌最近的小鬼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你知道激怒我\N有什么后果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擂台在我的工厂内\N在比赛前这小鬼放在我这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.28,0:10:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即来啊,工厂啊!\N我在工厂等你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心\N我很快会来救你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.90,0:10:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟激怒马之介真是个蠢材!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会遇到很惨的事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要连累我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛好像很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.17,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不关我事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.68,0:10:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得真轻松\N激怒那家伙会这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.19,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题!\N那样的家伙我会收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.40,0:11:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,你说得真好,年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长…长老大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长老大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.50,0:11:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样\N渡从长老大人那处打听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括被迫买工厂运来\N那喝不了的熔岩饮料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有极寒之剑\N在那燃烧岛上的事也知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.32,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?\N你便是传说中的救世主吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么出名吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难为情呢\N要我签名便糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.60,0:11:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要得意!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.58,0:11:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是长老大人\N要怎样才能渡过那个岛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.75,0:11:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把塞子打开便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞子是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.96,0:11:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地下水的塞子\N地点就在地厂的附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它拔出来的话\N地下水便会飞出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直达那岛上去成为一条水桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.50,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水桥吗?好,师傅\N在我和马之介比赛时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和古拿玛\N去打开地下的塞子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N你是要引开马之介的注意吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先说明,那家伙可是\N专业摔角手中的专业啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.21,0:12:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是在班中摔角第一的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂得很多招式的\N怎样啊?混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很强呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管来吧,混蛋\N怎样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人注目的一战\N我是渡对马之介的旁述多吏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天因解说的崎阪先生休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.25,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以由马之介先生的人质\N火美子小姐代为解说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛开始了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由熔岩商业提供的\N摔角比赛要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.68,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红方的是重77磅的\N挑战者战部渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.33,0:13:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊?混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.75,0:13:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝方是402磅重的冠军\N亚普多阑·马之介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.50,0:13:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啊?混蛋,快放了\N火美子和被迫做苦工的村民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.88,0:13:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大口气\N在打倒我之后才说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来就来吧,你这混蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.53,0:13:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快比赛便会开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子小姐\N你对比赛有怎样的预想?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡很有趣很有型!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.87,0:13:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,你随便进攻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.50,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我来了,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.16,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!\N那么我便利用绳索出飞龙腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗?好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!\N我叫战神丸出来破坏它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.01,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话\N不是立即被人发现吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.83,0:14:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这个…\N战神丸也打不破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会知道这种事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…这是…因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.25,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用什么特别的工具\N好像打不开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们是不行的了\N回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.30,0:15:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是这样呢\N打开塞子时必须的东西是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道,很难呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨钝的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.50,0:15:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?小鬼\N还未到睡觉的时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神不错呢,你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样便不好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.20,0:15:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!飞起了,飞得很高!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.53,0:15:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么简单就玩完\N会对不起观众的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们再多看一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.13,0:15:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以\N攻击其他人是犯规的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.26,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.42,0:16:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火美子,你等我\N我现在救你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的弱点…\N要找出他的弱点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱点…他的弱点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.40,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼,因为有人阻止着\N救了你一命呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.96,0:16:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次不会了\N我要再三秒内收拾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.79,0:16:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?\N那不是三啊,是二啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了,我知道你的弱点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪里会有弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?那么这个怎样啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!\N九九八十一攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.75,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二二得四、二三得六\N三五一十五
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三六一十八、三七二十一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.50,0:16:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.32,0:16:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很怕数学得马之介\N一听到九九乘法便会头痛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.45,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜\N二二得四、二三得六…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很头痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.86,0:17:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九六五十四、九七六十三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九八七十二、九九八十一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我来了\N渡特级…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.85,0:17:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞龙踢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利者是渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!万岁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.85,0:17:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[熔岩金刚]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.77,0:17:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们尝尝这部\N熔岩金刚的特别招式吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.78,0:17:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个了!\N那个便是地下水的开盖器了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:17:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,抢那家伙的开盖器啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.75,0:18:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开盖器?好,小蛋\N去拖延著他吧,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么家伙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是舒服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.09,0:18:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,在下也要去电话亭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好,我也要去帮他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了吗?熔岩金刚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他看看你的特别招式\N夺命剪刀脚!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸,没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么大不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.60,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等,用犯规招式真卑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.24,0:19:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口!\N也让你尝尝我的攻击吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!等一等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那混蛋,只懂用犯规招式\N不能饶恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.22,0:19:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!龙神丸\N把那家伙打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.70,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗?废魔神,轰天炮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.78,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压下去,龙神丸,不要输!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋,试试这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋风腿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.80,0:20:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放手,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.65,0:20:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点啊\N战神丸,站起来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.10,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,只懂用卑鄙手段\N我不会输的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒头椿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.79,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1、2、3…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.27,0:20:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙神丸胜出!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦,还未分胜负呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.18,0:20:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登龙剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我记著啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.11,0:21:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!好像来不及了呢\N没法子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是水造的桥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.35,0:21:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要顺著这地下水的水流\N便能到达那个岛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,出发吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.25,0:21:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.87,0:21:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用飞的过去\N我才不想湿身呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多谢你们…


